description:
Known for their durability, quality, and precise fit, these cone wrenches will provide years of service. The Y-head design puts more material where it's needed for strength and durability. Thin enough to use on narrow adjusting cones, the long handle provides great leverage and comfort.

  • Made of hardened industrial-quality steel with a military grade phosphate finish
  • Precision sizing
  • Vinyl-dipped handle
name: Park Tool Shop Cone Wrench
